**Definitions**

For purposes of this License:

**"Competitive Product or Service"** means any product or service providing lending, borrowing, liquidity, or closely substitutable functionality that is materially similar in purpose or function to those provided by the Aave Protocol.

**"Derivative"** means any work that modifies, incorporates, is based upon, or would otherwise be considered a derivative work of, the Licensed Work, including under applicable copyright law.

**"Production Environment"** means an environment in which users interact with the Licensed Work using "live", real, economically meaningful or value-bearing digital assets.

**"Test Environment"** means an environment in which users interact with the Licensed Work using non-live test, simulated, or synthetic data.

